metadata.name: stock trading elf - bathroom
metadata.description:
<Stock trading elf series: 3>

「Tinya」 is elf, nevertheless she likes meat

"When I was living in the elven forest, it was forbidden to eat meat"

Saying that, Tinya ate the whole 2kg Tomahawk steak by herself

As a result, Tinya was forced to spend all afternoon in the bathroom

But she had stocks that she had to sell

Tinya said,

"If the timing of the sell is even slightly off, I will incur a huge loss!" 

she grabbed her stomach, had no choice but to sell the stock on the toilet
